Class DJIGimbalTypeDef

  • java.lang.Object
    • dji.sdk.api.Gimbal.DJIGimbalTypeDef

extends java.lang.Object

    DJIGimbalTypeDef

    This class file will contain some enums for gimbal, such as gimbal mode, calibration and so on. The enum could be used as the input parameters or some output parameter of a callback function.

    : V2.4.0
